@startuml svc-trail-management--get-trails-trail_id-conditions

!include ../theme.puml
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #d97706
}

header [[/microservices/svc-trail-management/#integration-context ⬆ svc-trail-management Integration Context]]

title GET /trails/{trail_id}/conditions\nGet current trail conditions\n<size:10><color:#7c3aed>ARCHITECT OVERRIDE — enriched with live weather correlation and safety assessment</color></size>

participant "Client" as Client [[/applications/]]
participant "API Gateway" as GW [[/actors/#api-gateway]] #E0F2FE
participant "svc-trail-management" as Svc [[/microservices/svc-trail-management/]] #FEF3C7
participant "Weather Svc" as WX [[/microservices/svc-weather/]] #F1F5F9
database "PostGIS" as DB [[/microservices/svc-trail-management/#data-store]] #FEF9C3

note over Svc
  [[/services/api/svc-trail-management.html View in Swagger UI]]
end note

Client -> GW : GET /trails/{trail_id}/conditions
activate GW #d97706
GW -> Svc : route request
activate Svc #d97706

Svc -> DB : SELECT * FROM trail_conditions\nWHERE trail_id = ?\nORDER BY reported_at DESC\nLIMIT 1
activate DB #FEF9C3
DB --> Svc : Latest condition report\n(status, safety_rating,\nlast_reported_at)
deactivate DB

== Live Weather Enrichment ==

Svc -> WX : [[/microservices/svc-weather/#get-weathercurrent-get-current-weather-conditions GET /weather/current]]\n(trail region coordinates)
activate WX #F1F5F9
WX --> Svc : Current conditions\n(temp, wind, precipitation,\nvisibility)
deactivate WX

note right of Svc : Merge stored conditions\nwith live weather data.\nApply safety thresholds:\n- Wind > 45 mph → CLOSED\n- Visibility < 0.25 mi → CLOSED\n- Precipitation HEAVY → CAUTION\nReturn composite status

Svc --> GW : 200 OK\n(trail_id, status,\nsafety_rating, weather_snapshot,\nlast_updated)
deactivate Svc
GW --> Client : 200 OK
deactivate GW

@enduml
